metadata.name: Taal Volcano by Sevi
metadata.description:
Single Edition 1/1

On January 12, 2020, Taal Volcano in Batangas, Philippines erupted from its main crater, spewing ash  across Calabarzon, Metro Manila, some parts of Ilocos Region and Central Luzon. Little did we know that this was just the beginning of the hardships we would face this year.

Taal Volcano by Sevi
Sevi Agregado
January 2020, 7 years old
